    "answer_id" : 23997880,
    "question_id" : 10117026,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Pretty concise solution with plain Java 8 using <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/stream/package-summary.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>java.util.stream</code></a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static &lt;T&gt; ArrayList&lt;T&gt; toArrayList(final Iterator&lt;T&gt; iterator) {\n    return StreamSupport\n        .stream(\n            Spliterators\n                .spliteratorUnknownSize(iterator, Spliterator.ORDERED), false)\n        .collect(\n                Collectors.toCollection(ArrayList::new)\n    );\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
