    "question_id" : 10117026,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In Java 8, you can use the new <code>forEachRemaining</code> method that's been added to the <code>Iterator</code> interface:</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Element&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\niterator.forEachRemaining(list::add);\n</code></pre>\n"
