    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>Without external dependency</strong>, here's a one-liner using Streams and java 16 toList().</p>\n<p>Given an <code>Iterator&lt;?&gt; iterator</code>:</p>\n<pre><code>List&lt;?&gt; list = StreamSupport.stream(Spliterators.spliteratorUnknownSize(iterator, 0), false).toList();\n</code></pre>\n"
